      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, i guess. but it feels like there's a lot of money just disappearing into nowhere. is there any way to see exactly how much of my money is going to interest vs principal in a table or something? i want to see the breakdown properly.",
      "source": "evaluator"
